\begin_layout Standard
The purpose of this document is to thoroughly describe the software requirements
 for the GPU N-Body Integration Toolkit (GPUNIT).
 The document includes an explanation of the purpose and intended use of
 GPUNIT, as well as a detailed summary of the functional and non-functional
 requirements of the software.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Scope
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
GPUNIT targets users interested in running quantitative astronomical experiments.
 The software will be usable by physics students and instructors, as well
 as theoretical and observational physicists.
 A user of GPUNIT is expected to possess a general understanding of physics.
\end_layout

